# --- Xilinx Vivado Hardware/Simulation Ignore Patterns ---

# Ignore the entire local simulation compilation output directory
Asynchronous_FIFO.sim/
Asynchronous_FIFO.cache/
Asynchronous_FIFO.hw/
Asynchronous_FIFO.ip_user_files/

# Ignore log and journal tracker files generated by the GUI
*.log
*.jou
*.pb
*.str

# Ignore heavy waveform databases and simulation executable targets
*.wdb
*.wdf
*.db
*.exe
*.obj
*.mem
*.reloc